title: 01/01/21 – DPS – Best Of - T.J. Houshmandzadeh and Rob Parker fill in for Dan Patrick
itunes:title: 01/01/21 – DPS – Best Of - T.J. Houshmandzadeh and Rob Parker fill in for Dan Patrick
description:
Rob Parker and T.J. Houshmandzadeh blast Notre Dame for their history of ineptitude in the College Football Playoff and question if the Fighting Irish have the resume to match their #4 overall ranking. They talk about what’s on the line for Justin Fields in Ohio State’s rematch with Clemson and debate whether or not the Buccaneers are truly a Super Bowl contender. Plus, which young quarterback has the most to prove in the postseason?
